  "HT_Text_FE_Menu_GameOverBehaviorExplanation": {
    "message": "After a game over, you can choose between (1) continuing from the most recent unsaved checkpoint or (2) reloading your last sacred statue save, as it happened in the original game. The latter wipes any recent, unsaved progress and requires better manual save discipline, adding another element of difficulty that some players may prefer."
